## 2. Description of Service

Nimbus is a mobile application that:
- Displays real-time weather information based on your location
- Generates AI-powered artistic wallpapers reflecting current weather conditions
- Allows you to save, share, and set generated images as device wallpapers
- Offers premium features through subscription plans and credit packages

